---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Projects | Bry Martinez">
  <section class="section">
    <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>
    <h1>Things I am building</h1>
    <p>
      This page works well for active projects, experiments, and case studies.
      You can keep short summaries here and link out to blog posts or notes that
      explain the technical details.
    </p>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Featured project</p>
        <h2>Project title</h2>
        <p>Describe what it is, why it matters, and what stack you used.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Writeup</p>
        <h2>Technical deep dive</h2>
        <p>Point readers to a related note or blog post for the full story.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

